  • Classes in org.deeplearning4j.nn.conf.layers.variational used by org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.layers 
    Class and Description
    ReconstructionDistribution
    The ReconstructionDistribution is used with variational autoencoders VariationalAutoencoder to specify the form of the distribution p(data|x).
    VariationalAutoencoder
    Variational Autoencoder layer See: Kingma & Welling, 2013: Auto-Encoding Variational Bayes - https://arxiv.org/abs/1312.6114 This implementation allows multiple encoder and decoder layers, the number and sizes of which can be set independently.
